                  <summary change="#add-summary">
                     1 copy of Kitāb al-azhār wa-majma‘ al-anwār al-malqūṭah min basātīin al-asrār majāmīʻ al-fawākih al-rūḥānīyah wa-al-thimār by Bharūchīi, Ḥasan ibn Nūḥ, d. 1533
                  </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_25849-item1">
